## üõ†Ô∏è How We Built It (Technical Stack)

### Backend (The Engine Room)

* **FastAPI:** Used for its speed and automatic data validation.
* **Pydantic:** Ensures every one of the 24 tools receives the correct data before processing.
* **Groq API:** Provides the LPU-powered speed (sub-50ms) for all text and voice tools.

### Frontend (The Studio Set)

* **Vanilla JS & HTML5:** No heavy frameworks were used to ensure the fastest possible loading times.
* **CSS Themes:** A custom "Cinematic" styling system that supports Light and Dark modes.
* **i18n.js:** A custom internationalization engine supporting 5 languages (EN, ES, FR, DE, HI).

